USAGE:
	./my_rpg [OPTIONS]

OPTIONs:
	-h	Print the usage and quit.

USER INTERACTIONS:
	Use the mouse to navigate through the menu.
	ZQSD:	move character.
	In fight:
		Enter:		 validate and continue.
		Arrow keys: 	 navigate between options.
		Esc:  		 cancel.

This game is still in WIP.
The fight zone is around North East (follow the way, monsters will appears in grass).